         <abstract id="aspace_ab6cfec16461fe431ccf179a4efe46a8">The collection contains photographs of Dwight Hall at Yale, which was known as the Old Library from 1889 to 1930. Included are interior and exterior views and views of the building taken during the various stages of the construction or demolition of the surrounding structures.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_274df0167cf34faa0ced7298ba95f01e">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_1bf9e200f26a7457de38965aff045ee4">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Dwight Hall, Yale University, Photographs (RU 610). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_551be532f2463d21980206b5a0ebec9a">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_8b2810aa575cc56b9caf4bcd11c4c7a8">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_90be93a2b4729d32deaa0f6fe90d717a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains photographs of Dwight Hall at Yale, which was known as the Old Library from 1889 to 1930. Included are interior and exterior views and views of the building taken during the various stages of the construction or demolition of the surrounding structures.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
